verses.text:
\w Give|strong="H3051"\w* unto the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d*, O ye \w mighty|strong="H1121"\w*, \w give|strong="H3051"\w* unto the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* \w glory|strong="H3519"\w* and \w strength|strong="H5797"\w*.  +  r 29.1  t ye mighty: Heb. ye sons of the mighty *

\w Give|strong="H3051"\w* unto the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* the \w glory|strong="H3519"\w* due unto his \w name|strong="H8034"\w*; \w worship|strong="H7812"\w* the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* in the \w beauty|strong="H1927"\w* of \w holiness|strong="H6944"\w*.  +  r 29.2  t the glory…: Heb. the honour of his name *  +  r 29.2  t in…: or, in his glorious sanctuary *

The \w voice|strong="H6963"\w* of the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* \add is\add* upon the \w waters|strong="H4325"\w*: the \w God|strong="H0410"\w* of \w glory|strong="H3519"\w* \w thundereth|strong="H7481"\w*: the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* \add is\add* upon \w many|strong="H7227"\w* \w waters|strong="H4325"\w*.  +  r 29.3  t many: or, great *

The \w voice|strong="H6963"\w* of the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* \add is\add* \w powerful|strong="H3581"\w*; the \w voice|strong="H6963"\w* of the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* \add is\add* full of \w majesty|strong="H1926"\w*.  +  r 29.4  t powerful: Heb. in power *  +  r 29.4  t full…: Heb. in majesty *

The \w voice|strong="H6963"\w* of the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* \w breaketh|strong="H7665"\w* the \w cedars|strong="H0730"\w*; yea, the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* \w breaketh|strong="H7665"\w* the \w cedars|strong="H0730"\w* of \w Lebanon|strong="H3844"\w*.

He maketh them also to \w skip|strong="H7540"\w* like a \w calf|strong="H5695"\w*; \w Lebanon|strong="H3844"\w* and \w Sirion|strong="H8303"\w* like a \w young|strong="H1121"\w* \w unicorn|strong="H7214"\w*.

The \w voice|strong="H6963"\w* of the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* \w divideth|strong="H2672"\w* the \w flames|strong="H3852"\w* of \w fire|strong="H0784"\w*.\f + \fr 29.7 \ft divideth: Heb. cutteth out\f*

The \w voice|strong="H6963"\w* of the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* \w shaketh|strong="H2342"\w* the \w wilderness|strong="H4057"\w*; the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* \w shaketh|strong="H2342"\w* the \w wilderness|strong="H4057"\w* of \w Kadesh|strong="H6946"\w*.

The \w voice|strong="H6963"\w* of the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* maketh the \w hinds|strong="H0355"\w* to \w calve|strong="H2342"\w*, and \w discovereth|strong="H2834"\w* the \w forests|strong="H3295"\w*: and in his \w temple|strong="H1964"\w* doth every one \w speak|strong="H0559"\w* of \add his\add* \w glory|strong="H3519"\w*.\f + \fr 29.9 \ft to calve: or, to be in pain\f*\f + \fr 29.9 \ft doth…: or, every whit of it uttereth, etc\f*

The 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* \w sitteth|strong="H3427"\w* upon the \w flood|strong="H3999"\w*; yea, the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* \w sitteth|strong="H3427"\w* \w King|strong="H4428"\w* for \w ever|strong="H5769"\w*.

The 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* will \w give|strong="H5414"\w* \w strength|strong="H5797"\w* unto his \w people|strong="H5971"\w*; the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* will \w bless|strong="H1288"\w* his \w people|strong="H5971"\w* with \w peace|strong="H7965"\w*.
